    <h1>Medical Branches and Information</h1>

    <div class="branch">
        <h2>General Medicine (Internal Medicine)</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Focuses on the diagnosis and non-surgical treatment of adult diseases. Deals with complex medical problems and provides comprehensive care.</p>
        <p><strong>Demand:</strong> High, due to the broad range of illnesses treated and an aging population.</p>
        <p><strong>Colleges:</strong></p>
        <ul class="college-list">
            <li>AIIMS, New Delhi</li>
            <li>Christian Medical College (CMC), Vellore</li>
            <li>Maulana Azad Medical College (MAMC), New Delhi</li>
            <li>King Edward Memorial (KEM) Hospital, Mumbai</li>
            <li>Postgraduate Institute of Medical Education and Research (PGIMER), Chandigarh</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Merit-based scholarships offered by individual colleges, central and state government scholarships for economically weaker sections, and private trust scholarships.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="branch">
        <h2>General Surgery</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Deals with surgical procedures for various diseases and injuries. Includes pre-operative, operative, and post-operative management.</p>
        <p><strong>Demand:</strong> High, as surgical interventions are crucial for many conditions.</p>
        <p><strong>Colleges:</strong></p>
        <ul class="college-list">
            <li>AIIMS, New Delhi</li>
            <li>CMC, Vellore</li>
            <li>MAMC, New Delhi</li>
            <li>Seth GS Medical College, Mumbai</li>
            <li>JIPMER, Puducherry</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Similar to General Medicine, merit-based and need-based scholarships are available.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="branch">
        <h2>Pediatrics</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Specializes in the medical care of infants, children, and adolescents. Focuses on their growth, development, and specific health needs.</p>
        <p><strong>Demand:</strong> High, due to the importance of child health and the large pediatric population.</p>
        <p><strong>Colleges:</strong></p>
        <ul class="college-list">
            <li>AIIMS, New Delhi</li>
            <li>CMC, Vellore</li>
            <li>Lady Hardinge Medical College (LHMC), New Delhi</li>
            <li>Institute of Child Health, Kolkata</li>
            <li>Bangalore Medical College and Research Institute (BMCRI), Bangalore</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Merit-based and need-based scholarships, with specific scholarships for women in medicine.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="branch">
        <h2>Obstetrics and Gynecology (OB/GYN)</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Focuses on women's reproductive health, pregnancy, childbirth, and related medical conditions.</p>
        <p><strong>Demand:</strong> High, as women's health is a crucial aspect of healthcare.</p>
        <p><strong>Colleges:</strong></p>
        <ul class="college-list">
            <li>AIIMS, New Delhi</li>
            <li>CMC, Vellore</li>
            <li>MAMC, New Delhi</li>
            <li>King George's Medical University (KGMU), Lucknow</li>
            <li>Stanley Medical College, Chennai</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Merit and need-based, with scholarships often available for women pursuing OB/GYN.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="branch">
        <h2>Orthopedics</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Deals with the musculoskeletal system, including bones, joints, ligaments, tendons, and muscles. Focuses on diagnosis, treatment, and rehabilitation of injuries and disorders.</p>
        <p><strong>Demand:</strong> High, due to increasing sports injuries, accidents, and age-related musculoskeletal problems.</p>
        <p><strong>Colleges:</strong></p>
        <ul class="college-list">
            <li>AIIMS, New Delhi</li>
            <li>CMC, Vellore</li>
            <li>KEM Hospital, Mumbai</li>
            <li>Madras Medical College (MMC), Chennai</li>
            <li>Nizam's Institute of Medical Sciences (NIMS), Hyderabad</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Merit and need based scholarships are available.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="branch">
        <h2>Dermatology</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Specializes in the diagnosis and treatment of skin, hair, and nail conditions.</p>
        <p><strong>Demand:</strong> High, due to increasing awareness of skin health and cosmetic dermatology.</p>
        <p><strong>Colleges:</strong></p>
        <ul class="college-list">
            <li>AIIMS, New Delhi</li>
            <li>PGIMER, Chandigarh</li>
            <li>Bangalore Medical College and Research Institute (BMCRI), Bangalore</li>
            <li>Grant Medical College, Mumbai</li>
            <li>Osmania Medical College, Hyderabad</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Similar to other branches, merit and need based scholarships.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="branch">
        <h2>Psychiatry</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Focuses on the diagnosis, treatment, and prevention of mental, emotional, and behavioral disorders.</p>
        <p><strong>Demand:</strong> Increasing, as mental health awareness grows.</p>
        <p><strong>Colleges:</strong></p>
        <ul class="college-list">
            <li>NIMHANS, Bangalore</li>
            <li>AIIMS, New Delhi</li>
            <li>Institute of Human Behaviour and Allied Sciences (IHBAS), Delhi</li>
            <li>Christian Medical College (CMC), Vellore</li>
            <li>King George's Medical University (KGMU), Lucknow</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Merit and need based scholarships, with some specific to mental health fields.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="branch">
        <h2>Radiology</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Uses imaging technologies (X-rays, CT scans, MRIs, ultrasounds) to diagnose and treat diseases.</p>
        <p><strong>Demand:</strong> High, as imaging is essential for diagnosis.</p>
        <p><strong>Colleges:</strong></p>
        <ul class="college-list">
            <li>AIIMS, New Delhi</li>
            <li>PGIMER, Chandigarh</li>
            <li>CMC, Vellore</li>
            <li>MAMC, New Delhi</li>
            <li>Sanjay Gandhi Postgraduate Institute of Medical Sciences (SGPGIMS), Lucknow</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Merit and need based scholarships.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="branch">
        <h2>Anesthesiology</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Manages pain and provides anesthesia during surgical procedures and other medical interventions.</p>
        <p><strong>Demand:</strong> High, as anesthesia is crucial for surgeries and many procedures.</p>
        <p><strong>Colleges:</strong></p>
        <ul class="college-list">
            <li>AIIMS, New Delhi</li>
            <li>CMC, Vellore</li>
            <li>KEM Hospital, Mumbai</li>
            <li>JIPMER, Puducherry</li>
            <li>Stanley Medical College, Chennai</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Merit and need based scholarships.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="branch">
        <h2>Ophthalmology</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Specializes in the diagnosis and treatment of eye diseases and vision problems.</p>
        <p><strong>Demand:</strong> High, due to increasing eye problems.</p>
        <p><strong>Colleges:</strong></p>
        <ul class="college-list">
            <li>AIIMS, New Delhi</li>
            <li>Regional Institute of Ophthalmology (RIO), Chennai</li>
            <li>LV Prasad Eye Institute, Hyderabad</li>
            <li>Government Medical College, Thiruvananthapuram</li>
            <li>SN Medical College, Agra</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Merit and need based scholarships.</p>
    </div>
